{"tid":864384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵CEO：國產列車更勝英日韓製造","createTime":"2018-10-16T07:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T07:55:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"12eb3a368851e14f2a873f2a96af5348214d73a9","tid":864384,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20150430/s00001/1430361624656?fbclid=IwAR2qC9-xPUfnAlWYr2AZJwPHBqW0foYLtVNQ6OsvDlhH1te6oCES5M7SGqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150430%2Fs00001%2F1430361624656%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qC9-xPUfnAlWYr2AZJwPHBqW0foYLtVNQ6OsvDlhH1te6oCES5M7SGqs&d=EhBP80KDfqtSfCVNn%2BWU%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=cf7d8c94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150430%2Fs00001%2F1430361624656%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2qC9-xPUfnAlWYr2AZJwPHBqW0foYLtVNQ6OsvDlhH1te6oCES5M7SGqs&h=dd57b223\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20150430/s00001/1430361624656?fbclid=IwAR2qC9-xPUfnAlWYr2AZJwPHBqW0foYLtVNQ6OsvDlhH1te6oCES5M7SGqs</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵新CEO：國產列車更勝英日韓製造 (10:38)<br />\n2015/4/30<br />\n<br />\n接替韋達誠任港鐵行政總裁的梁國權表示，港鐵近幾年引入的國貨列車，質素不差，表現更勝英國、西班牙及日韓製造的列車。<br />\n<br />\n梁國權接受《信報》專訪時表示，港鐵歷年來曾引入四批列車，首批來自英國，第二批即機場快線及東涌線列車，在西班牙生產，第三批將軍澳線列車是由日本及南韓製造，至近幾年引入的第四批列車則為國產。<br />\n<br />\n對於國貨質素問題，梁國權認為不差，表現更勝之前的三批列車，他指每次進行招標，都會加入新要求及條件，「列車質素愈來愈好是理所當然」。"},{"pid":"9d00a77369f517546f3193afcbbd2c3bedbf4294","tid":864384,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb3a627f26a397a0c3dbf1fa571fae8467d579f","tid":864384,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"氣味方面勝過英日韓"},{"pid":"e529ce72298b21db7e3398d5870b5edd0b8a5fe5","tid":864384,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"自欺欺人"},{"pid":"3b001bff577d39bed1b85cf773ca06300beffbcb","tid":864384,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"係咪指國產列車係壞車表現方面比其他更勝一籌?"},{"pid":"c3049b493da19044dddacd55d0fc27486cc051a5","tid":864384,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"睇下邊方面囉,喺閪冧嗰方面絕對係世界第一"},{"pid":"76b8222ba785e57add30ff2052709ab1c1dd8a60","tid":864384,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b001bff577d39bed1b85cf773ca06300beffbcb","tid":864384,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"係咪指國產列車係壞車表現方面比其他更勝一籌?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"港鐵今早4綫故障 , 仲唔係更勝一籌?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d9833be15c1e30a1f96f5b7f4137059deb2495","tid":864384,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"死亡人數勝英美日一籌"},{"pid":"8380257a6c499d4f62b64a303cbd90858b0e97e1","tid":864384,"uid":84128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:21:44.000Z","msg":"爆炸性方面的確係"},{"pid":"b4c500d5d6a7fe205cb47f4f8b48af87791e57d7","tid":864384,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff57562437f30b706b7039c9065ff467731a8f1f","tid":864384,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"壞既密度一流"},{"pid":"12ddb3de3b50a84a272144900459d8d949239d42","tid":864384,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"大陸零件都係抄外國，但